OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA motorist continued driving for two-
OL,8,Fand-half miles after a fatal collision
OL,9,Fwith a 12-year-old boy on a motorway,
OL,10,Fa jury has been told.
OL,12,FCallum Rycroft died from his injuries
OL,13,Fafter being hit by a car driven by
OL,14,FShahid Ilyas, 48, as he ran across the
OL,15,FM62 in West Yorkshire on 5 August.
OL,17,FProsecutors told Bradford Crown Court
OL,18,Fthat Mr Ilyas was not criminally
OL,19,Fresponsible for Callum's death.
