OL,4,Cfatal collision with boy, 12, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FBut they told a jury how Ilyas did not
OL,8,Fstop as soon as he safely could after
OL,9,Fthe collision, despite "massive
OL,10,Fdamage" to his windscreen which
OL,11,Fseverely impeded his view of the road.
OL,13,FThey said he did not report the
OL,14,Fincident to the police until the next
OL,15,Fday.
OL,17,FMr Ilyas denies a charge of dangerous
OL,18,Fdriving.
