OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FBut the prosecutor said Ilyas failed
OL,8,Fto stop when the motorway hard
OL,9,Fshoulder did resume and then passed a
OL,10,Flayby when he pulled off the M62.
OL,12,FMr Smith said that, when the defendant
OL,13,Feventually pulled into a service
OL,14,Fstation, he called his car hire
OL,15,Fcompany to arrange recovery of the
OL,16,Fvehicle but did not ring the police.
OL,18,FIt was his solicitor who called
OL,19,Fofficers the next day, he said.
