OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Smith said to the six men and six
OL,8,Fwomen on the jury: "What you'll have
OL,9,Fto determine in this case is whether
OL,10,Fthe defendant driving on was
OL,11,Fdangerous, whether he could have
OL,12,Fbrought the vehicle to a safe stop
OL,13,Fbefore he did."
OL,15,FHe said the defendant is likely to
OL,16,Fargue that he was "simply a man doing
OL,17,Fhis best in difficult circumstances".
