OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe jurors were shown photographs of
OL,8,Fthe damage to Ilyas's windscreen and
OL,9,Fthe front end of the car, and Mr Smith
OL,10,Fsaid the impact with Callum brought
OL,11,Fthe vehicle to "an effective
OL,12,Fstandstill".
OL,14,FHe said: "You simply cannot drive a
OL,15,Fcar safely in that condition."
OL,17,FMr Smith said the defendant's decision
OL,18,Fto drive on was "inherently unsafe and
OL,19,Fdangerous".
