OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FConcluding his opening statement, the
OL,8,Fprosecutor said: "We accept the
OL,9,Fdefendant did not kill Callum.
OL,11,F"We say he should not have driven on
OL,12,Fin the manner that he did."
OL,14,FIlyas, of Moorfield Chase, Farnworth,
OL,15,FBolton, denies one count of dangerous
OL,16,Fdriving.
OL,18,FThe trial continues.
